OL,3,CTeachers finally 'graduate' with
OL,4,Cdegree decades after leaving classroom
OL,6,FHelen Ford was in Sunderland for a
OL,7,Fgraduation ceremony recognising the
OL,8,Fhard work and lifetime achievements of
OL,9,F120 teachers
OL,11,FA group of North East teachers who
OL,12,Fleft the classroom decades ago have
OL,13,Ffinally been recognised for their
OL,14,Fstudies - and their years of service.
OL,16,FSunderland University has presented
OL,17,Fhonorary Batchelor of Education
OL,18,Fdegrees to 120 former students of the
OL,19,Fcity's teaching college.
