OL,3,CTeachers finally 'graduate' with
OL,4,Cdegree decades after leaving classroom
OL,6,FAt the time they studied, they were
OL,7,Fawarded a Certificate of Education but
OL,8,Fthe university felt it was high time
OL,9,Ffor an upgrade.
OL,11,FProfessor Lynne McKenna from
OL,12,FSunderland University, said: "Those
OL,13,Fteachers have given such a lot back to
OL,14,Four region and yet they have not been
OL,15,Fafforded the opportunity to study for
OL,16,Fa degree and as other universities
OL,17,Fwere doing this retrospectively we
OL,18,Fthought it would be a really nice
OL,19,Fthing to do, to celebrate those staff
OL,20,Fwho have given so much to the region."
