OL,3,CTeachers finally 'graduate' with
OL,4,Cdegree decades after leaving classroom
OL,6,FThe former students all studied at
OL,7,FSunderland College of Education
OL,8,FTeacher Training College, based at
OL,9,FLangham Tower.
OL,11,FAfter a series of changes over the
OL,12,Fdecades, the college eventually became
OL,13,Fpart of the university.
OL,15,FAmong those receiving a retrospective
OL,16,Fdegree was Graham Fraser who studied
OL,17,Fat the college between 1966 and 1969.
OL,19,FLike many others, he stayed in the
OL,20,Fcity to teach - becoming head of three
OL,21,Fschools.
