OL,6,F"Everybody has appreciated what the
OL,7,Funiversity has done today because it's
OL,8,Fbeen a long time coming," he told ITV
OL,9,FTyne Tees.
OL,11,FStudying at the same time as Mr Fraser
OL,12,Fwas Bridget Andrews, who also
OL,13,Fcollected her honorary degree.
OL,15,FThe pair were instrumental in
OL,16,Fcontacting other former students to
OL,17,Fspread the word about Monday's (18
OL,18,FMarch) ceremony.
