OL,6,F"We all finished our careers long ago
OL,7,Fand it was just such a nice surprise
OL,8,Fand indeed an honour so yes, we were
OL,9,Fall thrilled," she said.
OL,11,F"A lot of us have stayed in contact
OL,12,Ffor a long long time so it was lovely
OL,13,Fto see everybody that we still knew
OL,14,Fand remembered together."
